            <title>[PIG-4690] Union with self replicate join will fail in Tez</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-4690</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Found this while trying to get a reproducible script for a different issue. Not a user reported one, but a possibility nonetheless. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;A = LOAD &apos;x&apos;;&lt;br/&gt;
B = LOAD &apos;y&apos;;&lt;br/&gt;
C = UNION A, B;&lt;br/&gt;
D = JOIN C, A using &apos;repl&apos;;&lt;br/&gt;
DUMP D;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
